{"tid":1471784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"失民心?BBC報導813懶人包重點翻譯［我地贏到盡呀］","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:58:25.000Z","uid":43785,"like":70,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8db4519b05ab11ee6b1d4e704d335913249a75bf","tid":1471784,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"失民心?BBC報導懶人包重點翻譯：<br />\n<br />\n．示威者一邊向受影響旅客道歉，一邊用行李車堵塞離境大堂。<br />\n．事件升溫的原因是一位來自大陸的卧底公安<br />\n．香港警察為左解救公安，身穿防暴裝入機場揮警棍打示威者。<br />\n．示威者為解救被捕女士，攻擊警察，警察舉槍。<br />\n<br />\n報導對警察同政府不利，文明國家唔係白痴，又冇打死個公安，做咩自己擔心番轉頭?<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇１０個外國媒體，全部都係幫香港示威者，貶抑香港政府同警察。除非係出名無人睇既外國紅媒，先會屌示威者。<br />\n<br />\n請問咁多位失民心軍師，係咪睇得ＴＶＢ新聞太多？仲有呀，今日鬼門開，各位民心軍師記得爭取冥界居民支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49340584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49340584&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3cyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=9b98b8f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49340584&h=af83b7aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49340584</a>"},{"pid":"8841d5d754c6153808804f7c652fcc7defdfd7a6","tid":1471784,"uid":153151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TaCGUSM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTaCGUSM.png&h=db157574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鳩sir"},{"pid":"ba53d26c0643ced9ae67f620c91f5ab6d79f3f28","tid":1471784,"uid":43785,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"今次贏到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不指責不割蓆 <br />\n我們一起走"},{"pid":"d9fb92e023a86c8376b3e4aff332845168d3a102","tid":1471784,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB